{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"91086-dia-de-sorte-do-hamisi","title":"Dia De Sorte Do Hamisi","description":"Hamisi goes to buy his uniform and spots a shirt he wants. His father says he doesn't have the money for it. What will happen to Hamisi's wish?","language":"Portuguese","langCode":"pt","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Marcella Selwyn","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Rob Owen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/91086-dia-de-sorte-do-hamisi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130943/size3/4301ba557d8658d098e9b0c3cde586a2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130943/size6/4301ba557d8658d098e9b0c3cde586a2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128393/size6/3b814a22e04f94a3da806ed0d4bfe9e8.jpg","text":"Hamisi precisa de um novo uniforme escolar.Seu pai o leva ao mercado.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128394/size6/526d93f337862dcf85f78b47d444097a.jpg","text":"Hamisi vê um menino usando uma camisa bonita. \"Essa é uma camisa muito elegante\", pensa Hamisi.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128395/size6/c59c72ae8fffa8e21438f443345eea50.jpg","text":"\"Eu gostaria de ter uma camisa como a daquele menino\", diz Hamisi.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128396/size6/a9a1625a815da51dbf82493210caae90.jpg","text":"\"Olha, ela está vendendo aquelas camisas especiais\", diz Hamisi. \"Pai, por favor, compra uma para mim\", ele pede.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128397/size6/a509b9803eb2d5fd1da587a898ab1346.jpg","text":"\"Hamisi, tenho que comprar seu uniforme,\" diz o pai.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128398/size6/13af50e7aac54ba06c3c69893e6f116c.jpg","text":"\"Não tenho dinheiro suficiente para essa camisa\", diz o pai.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128399/size6/f9cdd8511bdc8140560b5916970beab3.jpg","text":"O pai de Hamish paga pelo uniforme. Ele se surpreende quando ele recebe o troco. Há bastante dinheiro sobrando para comprar uma camisa!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128400/size6/f961da4690551e1359c0c43ef6106e8d.jpg","text":"É dia de sorte do Hamisi! Que camisa ele vai escolher?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":111}}